ving arrangement, in this state.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(2)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The person aged out of foster care after reaching eighteen years of age and subsequently voluntarily applied for placement with an individual licensee or approved kinship caregiver under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapter 237}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, or for placement in a supervised apartment living arrangement, in this state.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The person has demonstrated a willingness to participate in case planning and to complete the responsibilities prescribed in the person\u8217\'3fs case permanency plan.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The department has made an application for the person for adult services upon a determination that it is likely the person will need or be eligible for services or other support from the adult services system.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{2.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fDepartment\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ means the department of health and human services.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{3.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fDirector\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ means the director of health and human services.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{4.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fFood programs\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ means the supplemental nutrition assistance program and donated foods programs authorized by federal law under the United States department of agriculture.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{5.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fSupplemental nutrition assistance program\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ or }}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fSNAP\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ means benefits provided by the federal program administered through }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\cf1{7 C.F.R. pts. 270 }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\cf1{\u8211\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\cf1{ 283}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, as amended.}}}\par}{}{}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{[C71, 73, 75, 77, 79, }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{81}}}{, }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{S81, \'a7234.1}}}{; }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{81 Acts, ch 7, \'a711}}}{]}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{83 Acts, ch 96, \'a7160}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 86 Acts, ch 1245, \'a71419}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 92 Acts, ch 1229, \'a720}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 93 Acts, ch 54, \'a73}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2008 Acts, ch 1073, \'a71}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2009 Acts, ch 41, \'a7263}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2022 Acts, ch 1096, \'a72}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2023 Acts, ch 19, \'a7669}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2023 Acts, ch 112, \'a756}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2024 Acts, ch 1170, \'a7413}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2025 Acts, ch 135, \'a78}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\keep\keepn\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0\cbpat2{Referred to in }{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{\'a7217.36}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 235.1}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 237.1}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 238.1}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 252.14}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 425.15}}}\par}{}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj}{Subsection 1, paragraph a, subparagraphs (1) and (2) amended}\